<subSubSection id="2DB33CAE19E5A2D82B94C1E4CFB0669C" pageId="18" pageNumber="35" type="type species">
<paragraph id="ABE224949432FD08734133BACFCDC099" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">Type species.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B3E35E325CD2CA877EA9099EFFDC3F13" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">
<taxonomicName id="E07C1EEFBBB1632AE13F7AED7891001C" authorityName="Fairmaire &amp; Germain" authorityYear="1858" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="35" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cupriceps">
<emphasis id="89E7D46ACA4CF211707B022159AE5D0B" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">Anthaxia cupriceps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Fairmaire &amp; Germain, 1858 by original designation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A1499E0E1C4758DCDE0D9E53E30DA3CE" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">
The genus was originally described by 
<bibRefCitation id="7564220EAEC582FB93E552A882170C7E" author="Holynski, R" journalOrPublisher="Elytron, Barcelona," pageId="28" pageNumber="45" pagination="163 - 167" refId="B25" refString="Holynski, R, 1989. The content and systematic position of Cylindrophora Solier, 1851 (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Elytron, Barcelona, 3: 163 - 167" title="The content and systematic position of Cylindrophora Solier, 1851 (Coleoptera, Buprestidae)." volume="3" year="1989">
<normalizedToken id="B413B4E4F0EF8DFA4B267F108424576C" originalValue="Hołyński">Holynski</normalizedToken>
(1989)
</bibRefCitation>
as a subgenus of 
<taxonomicName id="4DA8604C03CBBCEAEDA19EC96F033D8C" class="Hexapoda" family="Buprestidae" genus="Anthaxia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="35" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="07629163B290433FD2FF09523E70EAC2" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">Anthaxia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and it was upgraded to the genus level by 
<bibRefCitation id="C79BB39AED30EEAA964DB7CD7D6C0E8C" author="Bily, S" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" pagination="1 - 11" refId="B12" refString="Bily, S, 2004. Taxonomic studies on Anthaxiina Gory &amp; Laporte de Castelnau and Curina Holynski (Coleoptera: Buprestidae). Zootaxa 555: 1 - 11" title="Taxonomic studies on Anthaxiina Gory &amp; Laporte de Castelnau and Curina Holynski (Coleoptera: Buprestidae)." volume="555" year="2004">
<normalizedToken id="257F1DAC5539B10A7F1E9BA6E53A15CD" originalValue="Bílý">Bily</normalizedToken>
(2004)
</bibRefCitation>
. According to 
<bibRefCitation id="7CB3B7B501036FFC495A6BA3E810597B" author="Bellamy, CL" journalOrPublisher="Folia Heyrovskyana, Supplementum" pageId="27" pageNumber="44" refId="B3" refString="Bellamy, CL, 2008. A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 3. Buprestinae: Pterobothrini through Agrilinae: Rhaeboscelina. Pensoft series faunistica No. 78, Sofia - Moscow, pp. (1-2) + 1261-1932." title="A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 3. Buprestinae: Pterobothrini through Agrilinae: Rhaeboscelina. Pensoft series faunistica No. 78, Sofia - Moscow, pp. (1 - 2) + 1261 - 1932." year="2008">Bellamy (2008)</bibRefCitation>
it contains 18 species but the division to several subgenera is necessary. Three species were transferred to the separate, monotypic genera (
<taxonomicName id="F38F230EA7E7E77E5578E0032DE813D1" authorityName="Bílý" authorityYear="2013" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Charlesina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="35" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B88E0C20F48AB44E7E4B962C93538C5A" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">Charlesina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gen. n., 
<taxonomicName id="352DEE0448802906DEDCED4D91C944E7" authorityName="Bílý" authorityYear="2013" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Cobosina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="35" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="13A41BCB3A40909EB6D26614464BD436" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">Cobosina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gen. n. and 
<taxonomicName id="E2A47AF9D65E8D4C70047887A60B457F" authorityName="Bílý" authorityYear="2013" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Marikia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="35" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="783EB33C3B3ABF17272DBA58CFC520FA" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="35">Marikia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gen. n. - see above), the remaining 15 species is assigned into three subgenera.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
